name\";s:23:\"Exclude pages from menu\";s:4:\"desc\";s:194:\"Enter a comma-separated list of the <a href\'http://faq.wordpress.com/2008/05/29/how-to-find-page-id-numbers/\'>page ID\'s</a> that you\'d like to exclude from the main top navigation. (ie. 1,2,3,4)\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"woo_menupages\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";}i:9;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:10:\"Intro text\";s:4:\"desc\";s:65:\"Enter your intro text for use on the front page. HTML is allowed.\";s:2:\"id\";s:9:\"woo_intro\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"textarea\";}i:10;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:21:\"Featured Slider Pages\";s:4:\"desc\";s:188:\"Enter a comma-separated list of the <a href\'http://faq.wordpress.com/2008/05/29/how-to-find-page-id-numbers/\'>page ID\'s</a> that you\'d like to display in the featured slider. (ie. 1,2,3,4)\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"woo_featpages\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";}i:11;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:23:\"Exclude From Navigation\";s:4:\"desc\";s:80:\"Check this box if you wish to exclude the slider pages from the main navigation.\";s:2:\"id\";s:16:\"woo_ex_featpages\";s:3:\"std\";s:4:\"true\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"checkbox\";}i:12;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:22:\"Featured Slider Height\";s:4:\"desc\";s:66:\"Enter the height of the featured slider (ie. 500). Default is 300.\";s:2:\"id\";s:14:\"woo_featheight\";s:3:\"std\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"text\";}i:13;a:2:{s:4:\"name\";s:13:\"Blog Settings\";s:4:\"type\";s:7:\"heading\";}i:14;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:33:\"Add Blog Link to Main Navigation?\";s:4:\"desc\";s:91:\"If checked, this option will add a blog link to your main navigation next to the Home link.\";s:2:\"id\";s:11:\"woo_addblog\";s:3:\"std\";s:5:\"false\";s:4:\"type\";s:8:\"checkbox\";}i:15;a:5:{s:4:\"name\";s:14:\"Blog Permalink\";s:4:\"desc\";s:237:\"Please enter the permalink to your blog parent category (i.e. /category/blog/). If you are not using <a href=\'http://codex.wordpress.org/Using_Permalinks\'>Pretty Permalinks</a> then you can use (/?ca